data.description: Stunning 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom home on almost 3/4 acre wooded lot. This open concept floor plan creates a wonderful gathering area for family and friends with wood look tile flooring through the main areas. Living offers gas fireplace with beautiful mantle, and large windows for natural light. Gorgeous kitchen features beautiful cabinetry all the way to the ceiling, a large kitchen island, granite countertops and a walk-in pantry. The kitchen opens to a beautiful well-lit breakfast area offering access to the huge vaulted covered patio making it a perfect home for outdoor entertaining. Your amazing master suite featuring high ceilings and a relaxing master bathroom with a dual-sink vanity, soaking tub, separate shower and a huge walk-in closet. Storm shelter in garage floor. Blinds throughout. Both garage doors have openers. Easy access to I-35 close enough to the city for convenience, but with all the benefits of peaceful country living.
